'Tis hard that thoſe that are Sequeſter'd to the Government, ſhould not be ſuffer'd ſo much as to Live; We are loath to ſay, had their Lives been loſt where the blood muſt have layn; and their Death had been unavoidable, had not the poor Gentlemen been able to deſcribe the Hue and Shape of theſe Monſters, and we hope it may Come to Light who lick't them into Evidence,
